  "text": "Probe specificity was confirmed in pilot studies by combining the irrelevant probe nonEub338-FITC with Eub338-Cy-3, and through hybridization experiments with pure isolates of Clostridia, Bacteroides, Enterobacteriaceae, and E. coli to screen for non-selective hybridization. Archived sections of gastric mucosa from a dog diagnosed with Helicobacter infection was used as a positive control for helicobacter FISH [CITATION_1] .",
